    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. u mentioned the \"long-term benefits\" vs \"short-term costs\"—but for a small shop in my district, those \"short-term\" costs might actually be enough to put them out of business entirely. do u think the government's focus on these long-term goals is kind of ignoring the actual economic reality for these local businesses right now?",
